[33mcommit dad1038de1f3ec51b6d9bb8c83c8ef84e03ab910[m
Author: lamat1111 <65860122+lamat1111@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Mon Sep 15 14:40:50 2025 +0200

    Fix race conditions in NewDirectMessageModal and SpaceEditor
    
    Fix inconsistent saving behavior in two additional modals that had the same
    race condition pattern as ChannelEditor. Both modals were calling async
    operations without awaiting them, then immediately closing the modal.
    
    NewDirectMessageModal:
    - Fix messageDB.saveConversation() race condition
    - Add proper error handling for conversation save failures
    - Ensure modal only closes after save completion
    
    SpaceEditor:
    - Fix updateSpace() race condition
    - Add proper error handling for space update failures
    - Prevent modal closure if save operation fails
    
    These fixes ensure data integrity and prevent loss of user changes due to
    premature modal dismissal during async operations.

[33mcommit d89ff30b33ecc90f23373e77023de37b2182137e[m
Author: lamat1111 <65860122+lamat1111@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Mon Sep 15 14:34:44 2025 +0200

    Fix ChannelEditor toggle save race condition
    
    Fix inconsistent saving of "pin to top" and "read only" toggles in ChannelEditor.
    The modal was dismissing immediately after calling saveChanges() without waiting
    for the async operations to complete, causing a race condition where changes
    could be lost if the save failed.
    
    - Add proper error handling in handleSave callback
    - Only dismiss modal after successful save completion
    - Prevent modal closure if save operation fails

